VT 2.35 (C) 


Great German killer.  Find almost all virus, but there's still german text
in the  program. VT looks at  first sight a little confusing, but when you
worked a little with  it, it all becomes clear.  Devs is  devices, so look
there for  Df0:, Df1:, Df2: and so on.  VT doesn't check a disks BB by it-
self when inserted, so you have to do it manually.

