beginner in viruskilling get's confused sometimes.  This killer is easy to
use, with lot's of fine graphics, but that's all!  A lot of viruses passes
by this  killer, (and I  suggest you  do too), and it's even  a commercial
virus-killer!  MAXON should have made it better in stead of using a lot of
diskspace with their weird configuration (Anti-Pirat Anti-VirusKiller???).
